name: SubDown
body:
Python script to download english subtitles for most movie/tv series episode.
NOTE: Works only with python 2.7.x and not 3.x
Forked from https://github.com/manojmj92/subtitle-downloader
Dirs:
	testing\ 
		it consists of some random code snippets


to create exe use 
python setup.py py2exe
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
